{"tid":353491,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[吹奏] 藝人眼中的偶像 全盛時期既IU","createTime":"2017-08-09T15:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T15:47:28.000Z","uid":34643,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"635540f62e111f5a7cde091e0542f329567fd284","tid":353491,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"無錯, 全盛時期就係而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n專輯主打大盤點:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SbeTuBQaJJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSbeTuBQaJJ8&d=DJesqidDmerScbpUKvI81ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=385bdc3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SbeTuBQaJJ8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/69039837ly1fidt3eocp6j20kt0xcdj5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F69039837ly1fidt3eocp6j20kt0xcdj5.jpg&h=3529ad89&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/69039837ly1fidt3eyg7kj20ke0xfdk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F69039837ly1fidt3eyg7kj20ke0xfdk5.jpg&h=dc9a9d70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d38a1f33c62d45dba1d75b898d75a78a809db5cd","tid":353491,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DGxs37DUwAEQZ6g.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDGxs37DUwAEQZ6g.jpg%3Alarge&h=a0bbfd99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb9fbbf85f3544883f4899bb3348dc8e1ae94888","tid":353491,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:38:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">眾明星一致贊揚的IU的歌曲是？？</span></div><br />\n<br />\n​​淪陷於三月份公開的歌手iu的歌曲【夜晚的信】的明星們十分多。<br />\n<br />\n歌手Jessica9日在一個媒體采訪中說到自己愛聽的k-pop是IU的歌曲。她說&ldquo;IU的歌曲怎麼聽都覺得全都很好聽&rdquo;，並說&ldquo;聽了最近剛發布的&lt;夜晚的信&gt;和&lt;palette&gt;&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&lt;夜晚的信&gt;是IU在正規4輯&lt;palette&gt;發布之前公開的歌曲,承載著淡淡的旋律和抒情的歌詞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMly1fierv64p37j30gk099glz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMly1fierv64p37j30gk099glz.jpg&h=1a60dcd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU在JTBC綜藝&lt;孝利家民宿&gt;中說&lt;palette&gt;中她最喜歡的歌就是&lt;夜晚的信&gt;。這集節目中聽了&lt;夜晚的信&gt;的孝利贊嘆道&ldquo;太好聽了，你的聲音和歌詞很搭。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n還有哪些明星稱贊了IU&lt;夜晚的信&gt;呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>作曲家金伊娜&ldquo;歌詞寫的實在是太好了&rdquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMly1fierv6h7blj30gk0k2q3w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMly1fierv6h7blj30gk0k2q3w.jpg&h=e021911b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作曲家金伊娜在&lt;夜晚的信&gt;公開後馬上在自己的sns中說&ldquo;哎呀真的唱的太好聽了，歌詞寫的太好了，太喜歡你了。&rdquo;並截圖下載&lt;夜晚的信&gt;的畫面發布。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>昭宥，佳仁，全素敏，劉在煥&ldquo;歌曲太好了&rdquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMly1fierv6tls4j30gk0qxmxg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMly1fierv6tls4j30gk0qxmxg.jpg&h=35524e5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMly1fierv77bd6j30gk0ckq42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMly1fierv77bd6j30gk0ckq42.jpg&h=1b0fb83e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外還有sistar昭宥，歌手佳仁，演員全素敏，歌手劉在煥連續在sns中表達了對&lt;夜晚的信&gt;的喜愛。特別是劉在煥說&ldquo;&lt;夜晚的信&gt;好似在五線譜裡畫出了音符這樣的星星，使這些星星成為了星座的人就是IU。&rdquo;表達了自己與眾不同的飯心。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>最近演員樸寶劍在自己的fancafe裡向粉絲推薦了&lt;夜晚的信&gt;。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMly1fierv7lezyj30gk0jy3z5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMly1fierv7lezyj30gk0jy3z5.jpg&h=8b2a078e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>親自唱了&lt;夜晚的信&gt;的藝人？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMly1fierv7zo60j30gk09aq3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMly1fierv7zo60j30gk09aq3q.jpg&h=b421ff7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五月出演了kbs2tv&lt;柳熙烈de寫生簿&gt;的龍俊亨說&ldquo;最近常聽IU的&lt;夜晚的信&gt;&rdquo;並將&lt;夜晚的信&gt;用自己的感覺分析後演唱了。<br />\n<br />\n還有歌手姜敏京,演員aliee，EXID正花通過sns上傳了唱&lt;夜晚的信&gt;的視頻。<br />\n<br />\n『cr:KBS 주요뉴스  翻譯:jessie』​​​​"},{"pid":"a046bc3a870001cc5e41f34f4f94394072cd7f3d","tid":353491,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"連天氣播報員: 寧靜的夏夜與&quot;夜信&quot;很配<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/0066GajVgy1fieoedttyfj30nm0d6t9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F0066GajVgy1fieoedttyfj30nm0d6t9b.jpg&h=8e665d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f44ea7f0a61311ad4475cefaef03fa0cbffa59eb","tid":353491,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T14:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DG1gSxrUQAAeotx.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDG1gSxrUQAAeotx.jpg%3Alarge&h=8b317462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DG0ntTlXYAAr5U9.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDG0ntTlXYAAr5U9.jpg%3Alarge&h=998cfcc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8c7357c148c8f95aa7b88dd1b394c10195e7a74","tid":353491,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DGmjFUfUAAAZpbS.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDGmjFUfUAAAZpbS.jpg%3Alarge&h=80eb81bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f5fbf48d3a9efbd4ba4b6ad023a3c5312fa4135","tid":353491,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T